description:
Minor amendment of planning permission ref: P062161 dated 23/03/2007.  The amendments are:
A]	re-arrangement of basement car-park layout, provision of 7 motorcycle spaces, alteration of biomass enclosure, and replacement of vehicle access ramp with car-lift;
B]	alteration to internal layout of dwellings, circulation space and access cores;
C]	addition, removal and rearrangement of window and door arrangements;
D]	alteration and reduced width of balconies, amendment to the building line of the rear elevations and installation of vents; and
E]	increase in building height and amendment of parapet detail.
